      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": [
        "prompt examples:\nRelight the image using noon sunlight (neutral color temperature, strong light, clear shadows).\n\nRelight the image using warm sunset sunlight, lower color temperature (3500K), soft light, elongated shadows, with golden highlights.\n\nRelight the image with natural diffuse light of an overcast day, almost no shadows, slightly cool color temperature (6500K), evenly soft lighting.\n\nRelight the image with natural side light from a window, one side is bright, the other gently dim, with clear layered contrast.\n\nRelight the image with moonlight, higher color temperature (8000K), subtle blue tint, slight sheen in the dark areas.\n\nRelight the image using three-point lighting: key light, fill light, back light; emphasize facial structure and enhance separation from the background.\n\nRelight with candlelight, low color temperature (2500K), yellow warm tone, strong central light, dark surroundings.\n\nRelight with neon lights, multicolored sources (pink and blue), high contrast, strong nighttime ambiance.\n\nRelight with soft light in morning fog, cool color temperature (7000K), low contrast, slight halo effect.\n\nprompt examples (ch):\n重新照明,使用正午阳光（色温中性，光线强烈，阴影清晰）的光线对图片进行重新照明\n\n使用傍晚的暖色阳光重新照明，色温较低（3500K），柔和光线，阴影拉长，带有金色高光\n\n使用阴天的自然漫射光重新照明，几乎没有阴影，色温略冷（6500K），光线均匀柔和\n\n使用从窗户射入的自然侧光重新照明，一侧明亮，另一侧柔和暗淡，层次分明\n\n使用月光重新照明，色温较高（8000K），带有微弱的蓝色调，暗部带轻微光泽\n\n使用三点布光重新照明：主光、辅光、逆光，突出面部结构，增强与背景的分离感\n\n使用烛光重新照明，色温低（2500K），偏黄暖色调，中央光强，周围昏暗\n\n使用霓虹灯重新照明，多色光源（粉色、蓝色），高反差，夜色氛围浓烈\n\n使用清晨雾气中的柔光重新照明，色温冷（7000K），低对比度，带轻微光晕\n\n"
      ],
